abstract: Strange, according to Mr. De Visme Shaw, is the derivation of the word "snipe." The birds of the Scolopax genus are distinguishable by the length of their bills. Now the French for bill is bec, hence becassine. abstract: A STONE arch bridge with a clear span of 295 feet is now in process of construction at Plauen, in Saxony. abstract: HAVANA, Feb. 9. -- The last American garrison in Cuba has been abandoned, and the American military occupation has passed completely into history. The occurrence threw a gloom over some of the Cubans present, who took it as an evil omen.

abstract: The Mayor has approved the action of the Civil Service Commission of the city in abolishing competition for the place of Deputy Tax Commissioner.
